narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Future Age Inc. is a Non-emergency Medical Transport (VAN) provider based in Cleveland, OH. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $18.5M in Medicaid payments across 344K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $18.5M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
